This is the README file for Language::SIOD, a module that provides
Perl bindings to SIOD, a small-footprint Scheme implementation.

Please type "perldoc Language::SIOD" after installation to
see the module usage information.

* Installation

Language::SIOD uses the standard perl module install process:

cpansign -v		# optional; see SIGNATURE for details
perl Makefile.PL
make			# or 'nmake' on Win32
make test
make install

